# ─── Rust ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/target

# ─── Node / Bun ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/

# ─── Logs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
bun-debug.log*
bun-error.log*

# ─── napi-rs build artifacts ─────────────────────────────────────────
# Both regenerated by `npm run build` (which napi build → napi-rs macro
# expansion → writes them next to this Cargo.toml). Source of truth is
# `src/lib.rs`. The npm tarball picks these up via `package.json#files`,
# so git-tracked copies would only risk drifting from the source.
index.js
index.d.ts
/*.node
/npm

# ─── TypeScript ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.tsbuildinfo

# ─── OS / editor cruft ───────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
